00:19:12,268 --> 00:19:14,588
Ja-Oh’s not only good at talking,

275
00:19:14,588 --> 00:19:15,143
she’s also a s—

276
00:19:18,266 --> 00:19:18,870
What is it?

277
00:19:20,266 --> 00:19:20,768
What is it?

278
00:19:20,768 --> 00:19:21,814
S– what?

279
00:19:23,706 --> 00:19:24,936
She’s rather pretty

280
00:19:26,747 --> 00:19:27,517
A sweet talker.

281
00:19:27,517 --> 00:19:28,257
Sweet?

282
00:19:28,681 --> 00:19:29,730
