283
00:19:30,424 --> 00:19:31,944
Nothing, Mom.

284
00:19:33,201 --> 00:19:34,531
Then. bring me everything.

285
00:19:34,531 --> 00:19:36,314
Please have it separately to eat with rice.

286
00:19:36,422 --> 00:19:37,236
Sure.

287
00:19:37,828 --> 00:19:39,163
Please wait a minute.

288
00:19:41,875 --> 00:19:42,418
Mai.

289
00:19:43,719 --> 00:19:45,783
This friend of yours is very diligent.

290
00:19:45,783 --> 00:19:47,672
You should look up to her as an example.

291
00:19:48,038 --> 00:19:52,249
