292
00:19:52,643 --> 00:19:53,356
That’s right.

293
00:19:53,876 --> 00:19:55,813
You have to try very hard.

294
00:19:55,813 --> 00:20:00,709
When you graduate, your grandmother will no longer have any worries.

295
00:20:00,709 --> 00:20:02,764
