297
00:20:09,303 --> 00:20:11,650
Me? Becoming a doctor?

298
00:20:13,584 --> 00:20:15,866
You’re the one who’s most fitting to become a doctor.

299
00:20:15,866 --> 00:20:18,261
When you graduate, you will get a job right away,

300
00:20:18,261 --> 00:20:21,687
