301
00:20:21,687 --> 00:20:22,572
Right.

302
00:20:22,572 --> 00:20:26,421
You’re saying something without considering your son’s intelligence.

303
00:20:28,579 --> 00:20:29,588
Then try hard.

304
00:20:29,588 --> 00:20:30,579
Try hard.

305
00:20:33,215 --> 00:20:34,716
I’m studying every day.

306
00:20:34,716 --> 00:20:35,232
Huh?

307
00:20:35,844 --> 00:20:37,324
I have a great dream.

308
00:20:38,186 --> 00:20:38,957
What dream?

309
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:43,329
I will become a world’s class magician.

310
00:20:45,237 --> 00:20:46,066
Oh?

311
00:20:46,976 --> 00:20:48,622
A word’s class magician?

312
00:20:50,681 --> 00:20:52,056
The one with this song, right?

313
00:20:55,199 --> 00:20:55,790
Honey.

314
00:20:59,588 --> 00:21:00,196
Honey.

315
00:21:02,039 --> 00:21:02,735
Honey!

316
00:21:04,031 --> 00:21:04,599
Enough!

317
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:08,112
[BABY BANK’S HOUSE]

318
00:21:11,496 --> 00:21:12,497
